---
title: Sesame Barramundi Rice Bowls with Mushrooms and Sriracha Mayo
description: Inspired by traditional gohan, Japanese stirred rice, this dish pairs flaky, sesame-crusted barramundi with heaps of delicious veggies and a fragrant, savoury ginger-soy sauce – all mixed together in one delicious bowl. A little spicy mayo on top adds a bright, creamy zing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sesame-barramundi-rice-bowls-e4ca764f.jpg
